尔巴基是这个团体的成员已出版的《数学原理》（约40卷）一书作者的笔名。他们以结构主义观点从事数学分析，认为数学结构没有任何事先指定特征，它是只着眼于它们之间关系的对象的集合。认为数学就是关于结构的科学。在各种数学结构之间有其内在的联系，其中代数结…","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/desc","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 992, 108)","boundsInScreen":"(44, 1420 - 1036, 1528)"},{"index":1,"text":"596赞同 · 50评论","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/extra_info","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 293, 48)","boundsInScreen":"(44, 1556 - 337, 1604)"},{"index":2,"resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/more","class":"android.widget.ImageView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 66, 66)","boundsInScreen":"(970, 1547 - 1036, 1613)"}]},{"index":7,"class":"android.view.ViewGroup","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":true,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 1080, 271)","boundsInScreen":"(0, 1657 - 1080, 1928)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"ZS Chen：2023年3月1日，星期三，晴 明天就是康托小学一年级二班第一节数学课了。要知道，我在高斯幼儿园里最喜欢的课就是数学课，我可是班里唯一能数到 [公式] 的小朋友呢！2023年3月2日，星期四，晴转多云 好好玩的数学课，开学前就听爸爸说，第一周的内容会是冯诺伊曼序数，这是小升初数学里最基础的部分。老师为了给我们打好基础，在第一节课花了好大心思，整整50分钟一句话都没有讲。下课之后，她才告诉我们，刚才这节课的内容就…","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/desc","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zh